<table class="row">
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td class="wrapper last">
        <table class="twelve columns">
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="panel panel-default">

                <h1 class="text-center">
                  Thanks for signing up for updates on <a href="<%= product_url(@product) %>"><%= @product.name %></a>!
                </h1>

                <p>
                  <%= @product.name %> is being built on <a href="<%= root_url %>">Assembly</a>, a platform for building open-source projects. A product's contributors receive a stake in the product through <a href="https://coins.assembly.com">Assembly Coins</a>. We'll send the most important updates straight from the core team to your inbox.
                </p>

                <hr>

                <p>
                  Since you signed up as a beta builder on the <a href="<%= product_url(@product) %>">Assembly Coins project</a>, an account has been reserved for you with 10 Coins &mdash; these digital tokens translate to a portion of Assembly Coins' future revenue.
                </p>

                <h4>
                  Why should you sign up?
                </h4>

                <ol>
                  <li>
                    You'll get access to more cool projects, like <a href="<%= product_url(Product.find_by_slug('buckets')) %>">Buckets</a>.
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    You can build Assembly Coins if you want &mdash; and earn more Coins in the process!
                  </li>

                  <li>
                    Did we mention that each project has its own Coin? You earn Coins based directly on your contributions to any of the projects on Assembly, which means real revenue for your work.
                  </li>
                </ol>

                <table class="container">
                  <tbody>
                    <tr>
                      <td>
                        <table class="row">
                          <tbody>
                            <tr>
                              <td class="wrapper">
                                <table class="twelve columns">
                                  <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                      <td>
                                        <table class="medium-button radius">
                                          <tbody>
                                            <tr>
                                              <td style="border-color: #428bca !important; background-color: #428bca !important;">
                                                <a style="color: #fff !important;" href="<%= new_user_registration_url(email: @email_address, assembly_assets_promotion: true) %>">Create your account and claim your Coins</a>
                                              </td>
                                            </tr>
                                          </tbody>
                                        </table>
                                      </td>
                                    </tr>
                                  </tbody>
                                </table>
                              </td>
                            </tr>
                          </tbody>
                        </table>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </tbody>
                </table>

                <br/>

                <p>
                  Over and out,
                  <br/>
                  The <%= @product.name %> team
                </p>

              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
